<subSubSection lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="122" pageId="9" pageNumber="121" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1877,2010]" lastBlockId="10.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="122" pageId="9" pageNumber="121">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,502,1985,2010]" pageId="9" pageNumber="121">Distribution and ecology.</emphasis>
It is distributed in Western Palearctic with only a few references from the Asiatic part (Martynova 1979, Babenko 2007). It was singly collected in the northern part of the Buryat Republic. This record is new for the area under study and is also the most eastern one for the species.
</paragraph>
